{
  "texts": [
    "Testing procedures that utilize artificial intelligence focus on medical imaging, including Xrays and computed tomography (CT), predictive analysis, and radiology.",
    "Remote scanning and automated image acquisition aid lab technicians in their work with minimal physical contact with suspected patients.",
    "Following contactless image acquisition, images were segmented to detect lung infections, supporting quantitative analysis and COVID-19 diagnosis.",
    "For instance, deep learning models such as UNet++, UNet, and VB-Net have been adopted for image segmentation.",
    "Additionally, the severity of the illness was forecasted, and AI-based treatment and monitoring were initiated for isolated patients."
  ]
}